CSAT_Score_1.label: CSAT_Score
CSAT_Score_1.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.SurveyQuestionResponse53.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by 'SurveyQuestion_QuestionType' == "Rating";Current = filter q by {{row(ActivityDate_1.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Year', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Month','SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Day')")}};Current = foreach Current generate first('NumberValue')/(first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue')) as 'Rating',first('Scale') as 'Scale';Previous = filter q by {{row(ActivityDate_2.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Year', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Month', 'SurveyResponse_CompletionDateTime_Day')")}};Previous = foreach Previous generate  first('NumberValue')/(first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue')) as 'PreviousRating', first('Scale') as 'Scale';result = group Current by all full, Previous by all;result = foreach result generate coalesce(round((sum(Current.'Rating')/count(Current)) * first(Current.'Scale'),2),0) as 'CSAT_Current',coalesce(round((sum(Previous.'PreviousRating')/count(Previous)) * first(Previous.'Scale'),2),0) as 'CSAT_Previous';result = foreach result generate 'CSAT_Current','CSAT_Previous',('CSAT_Current' - 'CSAT_Previous')/'CSAT_Previous' as 'Delta',case when CSAT_Current < 0 then "rgb(232, 67, 64)" else "rgb(58, 232, 103)" end as 'Bar_Color_CSAT';

lens_4.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.SurveyQuestionResponse53.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by 'SurveyQuestion_QuestionType' == "Rating";result = foreach q generate (first('NumberValue')/first('QuestionChoice_MaxValue')) * first('Scale') as 'CSATValue', count(q) as 'count';result = group result by all;result = foreach result generate round(sum(CSATValue)/sum(count),2) as 'Program_CSAT';
